00:59:28,774 --> 00:59:30,025
Hey.

782
00:59:30,109 --> 00:59:31,402
Laeddis.

783
00:59:33,028 --> 00:59:34,196
Yeah.

784
00:59:39,493 --> 00:59:40,578
My...

785
