01:03:21,757 --> 01:03:23,258
He isn't gone.

803
01:03:24,468 --> 01:03:26,053
He's still here.

804
01:03:28,347 --> 01:03:29,556
I know.

805
01:03:30,516 --> 01:03:32,017
