Now. Put it down.

818
01:04:38,125 --> 01:04:41,712
Grab him, grab him, grab him, grab him!
Get him, get him!

819
01:04:45,716 --> 01:04:48,802
You need to go find him
'cause he needs to be here.

820
01:04:48,844 --> 01:04:51,388
You think the whole electrical system
is fried?

821
01:04:51,471 --> 01:04:54,224
I'd say it's a good possibility, yeah.

822
01:04:54,308 --> 01:04:57,352
- All the electronic security, the fences...
- Why are you always running?

823
01:04:57,436 --> 01:05:00,647
- ...the gates, the doors.
- Why is it you every time? Come on.

824
01:05:00,689 --> 01:05:04,651
