people screaming day and night,

831
01:05:31,887 --> 01:05:34,598
no windows and iron bars everywhere.

832
01:05:34,681 --> 01:05:35,849
Watch your head!

833
01:05:56,161 --> 01:05:58,163
- Oh, Jesus Christ!
- Jesus.

834
01:05:58,455 --> 01:06:00,499
First time on Ward C, huh?

835
01:06:01,541 --> 01:06:03,251
- Yeah.
- Yeah. Yeah.

836
01:06:03,335 --> 01:06:04,378
We heard stories, but...

837
01:06:04,461 --> 01:06:07,089
Trust me, son, you haven't heard shit.

838
01:06:07,547 --> 01:06:09,716
We got most of the bugsies
locked down now,

839
01:06:10,050 --> 01:06:12,010
but some of them are still loose.

840
01:06:12,052 --> 01:06:14,763
And if you see one,
don't try to restrain him yourselves.

841
01:06:14,846 --> 01:06:17,224
These fuckers will kill you. Clear?

842
01:06:18,308 --> 01:06:21,228
All right, get your asses moving then.
Go on.

843
01:07:17,951 --> 01:07:19,286
He's here.

844
01:07:23,290 --> 01:07:26,710
Laeddis. I can feel him.

845
01:07:30,964 --> 01:07:32,758
Tag! You're it!

846
01:07:32,799 --> 01:07:34,801
Wait! Boss! Ted!

847
01:07:44,352 --> 01:07:46,021
Hey! Hey!

848
01:07:47,481 --> 01:07:48,648
Teddy.

849
01:08:30,607 --> 01:08:32,067
Listen to me.

850
01:08:33,151 --> 01:08:36,071
Listen, I don't wanna leave here,
all right?

851
01:08:36,530 --> 01:08:38,740
I mean, why would anybody want to?

852
01:08:38,824 --> 01:08:42,327
We hear things here
about the outside world.

853
01:08:42,369 --> 01:08:45,831
- About atolls, about H-bomb tests.
- Teddy, where are you?

854
01:08:45,872 --> 01:08:47,874
You know how a hydrogen bomb works?

855
01:08:47,958 --> 01:08:51,211
- I know. With hydrogen! With hydrogen.
- Ah, that's funny.

856
01:08:51,294 --> 01:08:54,214
- Boss!
- Other bombs explode, right?

857
01:08:55,048 --> 01:08:56,675
But not the hydrogen bomb.

858
01:08:56,716 --> 01:09:02,180
It implodes, creating an explosion
to the thousandth, the millionth degree!

859
01:09:02,639 --> 01:09:04,266
- Do you get it?
- Yeah! Yeah.

860
01:09:04,349 --> 01:09:05,934
- Do you?
- I get it, I get it!

861
01:09:06,017 --> 01:09:07,269
Let him go!

862
01:09:10,897 --> 01:09:11,982
No!

863
01:09:21,241 --> 01:09:23,243
No! No!

864
01:09:24,661 --> 01:09:26,413
What are you doing?

865
01:09:26,705 --> 01:09:29,416
Jesus Christ, Teddy. Jesus!

866
01:09:29,749 --> 01:09:31,001
Oh, you got Billings.

867
01:09:31,084 --> 01:09:33,587
What the fuck's
the matter with you guys?

868
01:09:33,670 --> 01:09:34,754
Catch them, not kill them!

869
01:09:34,838 --> 01:09:37,799
- He jumped us.
- You, give me a hand with him.

870
01:09:37,883 --> 01:09:40,302
We've gotta get him to the infirmary.
God damn it.

871
01:09:40,385 --> 01:09:42,971
No, no! Not you, not you. Take a walk.

872
01:09:43,513 --> 01:09:47,100
Come on. Cawley's gonna have
my goddamn balls for this.

873
01:10:18,048 --> 01:10:20,258
Laeddis.

874
01:10:40,487 --> 01:10:42,072
Laeddis.

875
01:10:53,124 --> 01:10:55,710
Stop me, please,

876
01:10:55,794 --> 01:10:57,337
before I kill more.

877
01:10:59,339 --> 01:11:01,841
Stop me before I kill more.

878
01:11:02,259 --> 01:11:04,177
Laeddis.

879
01:11:12,269 --> 01:11:14,187
Please, please.

880
01:11:18,441 --> 01:11:20,402
I see you all.

881
01:11:21,152 --> 01:11:24,531
Laeddis.

882
01:11:30,870 --> 01:11:33,623
You told me I'd be free of this place.

883
01:11:34,708 --> 01:11:36,626
You promised.

884
01:11:38,211 --> 01:11:39,671
You lied.

885
01:11:40,213 --> 01:11:41,548
Laeddis.

886
01:11:47,053 --> 01:11:48,388
Laeddis?

887
01:11:48,847 --> 01:11:51,433
That's pretty damn funny.

888
01:11:53,852 --> 01:11:56,396
- Your voice.
- Don't you recognize it?

889
01:11:57,689 --> 01:11:59,816
After all the talks we had?

890
01:12:00,734 --> 01:12:02,777
After all the lies you told me?

891
01:12:02,861 --> 01:12:04,654
Let me see your face.

892
01:12:05,155 --> 01:12:07,115
They say I'm theirs now.

893
01:12:08,241 --> 01:12:10,577
They say I'll never leave here.

894
01:12:11,828 --> 01:12:13,997
Your match is about to go out.

895
01:12:16,583 --> 01:12:19,336
- Let me see your goddamn face! Now!
- Why?

896
01:12:19,753 --> 01:12:21,212
So you can lie to me more?

897
01:12:22,088 --> 01:12:24,299
- This isn't about the truth.
- Yes, it is.

898
01:12:24,466 --> 01:12:27,969
- It's about exposing the truth.
