899
01:12:28,261 --> 01:12:29,763
And Laeddis.

900
01:12:31,097 --> 01:12:33,058
That's all it's ever been about.

901
01:12:34,142 --> 01:12:37,854
I was incidental. A way in.

902
01:12:41,191 --> 01:12:43,860
George... George Noyce.

903
01:12:45,028 --> 01:12:48,490
No. It's not possible. You can't be here.

904
01:12:48,573 --> 01:12:49,949
You like it?

905
01:12:51,659 --> 01:12:53,620
Who did this to you, George?

906
01:12:53,661 --> 01:12:54,913
You did.

907
01:12:55,455 --> 01:12:56,915
What the hell do you mean?

908
01:12:56,956 --> 01:13:01,127
All your talk. All your fucking talk,
and I'm back in here because of you.

909
01:13:01,211 --> 01:13:03,797
George, how did they get you
out of Dedham, huh?

910
01:13:03,880 --> 01:13:05,090
However this happened, I...

911
01:13:05,131 --> 01:13:07,133
I'm gonna find a way to fix this,
you understand me?

912
01:13:07,175 --> 01:13:11,096
