915
01:13:16,476 --> 01:13:19,270
Everything you were up to.
Your whole plan.

916
01:13:20,063 --> 01:13:23,733
This is a game. All of this is for you.

917
01:13:24,442 --> 01:13:28,905
You're not investigating anything.
You're a fucking rat in a maze.

918
01:13:30,281 --> 01:13:31,491
Georgie...

919
01:13:32,117 --> 01:13:35,245
