922
01:13:42,335 --> 01:13:44,087
You never worked with him before,
have you?

923
01:13:46,464 --> 01:13:48,883
He's a U.S. Marshal. He's...

924
01:13:48,967 --> 01:13:51,803
You never worked
with him before, have you?

925
01:13:54,597 --> 01:13:58,476
George, look, I know people.
I trust this man.

926
01:14:03,440 --> 01:14:05,442
Then they've already won.

927
01:14:08,403 --> 01:14:09,529
Fuck.

928
01:14:14,284 --> 01:14:17,328
And they're gonna take me
to the lighthouse.

929
01:14:18,955 --> 01:14:20,790
They're gonna cut into my brain.

930
01:14:22,250 --> 01:14:23,877
And I'm only here

931
01:14:24,210 --> 01:14:25,545
because of you!

932
01:14:26,588 --> 01:14:28,965
George, I'm gonna get you out of here.

933
01:14:29,048 --> 01:14:31,342
You're not going to the lighthouse.
You're not.

934
01:14:31,384 --> 01:14:34,179
You can't dig out the truth
and kill Laeddis at the same time.

935
01:14:34,220 --> 01:14:37,807
You gotta make a choice.
You understand that, don't you?

936
01:14:38,224 --> 01:14:41,227
