- Liar!

937
01:14:41,311 --> 01:14:44,397
I'm not gonna kill him, I swear to you!
I swear.

938
01:14:44,647 --> 01:14:46,024
She's dead.

939
01:14:47,066 --> 01:14:48,735
She... Let her go.

940
01:14:50,236 --> 01:14:51,613
Let her go.

941
01:14:52,614 --> 01:14:55,867
Tell him, Teddy.
Tell him why.

942
01:14:58,578 --> 01:15:01,247
You gotta do it.
There's no other way.

943
01:15:01,873 --> 01:15:03,416
- Let her go.
- Tell him about the day

944
01:15:03,458 --> 01:15:06,336
- you brought me my locket.
- You gotta do it!

945
01:15:06,419 --> 01:15:09,839
How I told you my heart was breaking
and you asked me why.

946
01:15:09,923 --> 01:15:12,800
She's fucking with your head.

947
01:15:12,884 --> 01:15:14,761
And I told you it was from happiness.

948
01:15:14,844 --> 01:15:17,305
She's gonna kill you.
She's gonna kill you.

949
01:15:20,350 --> 01:15:23,603
You wanna uncover the truth?
You gotta let her go.

950
01:15:25,772 --> 01:15:27,440
